data.text: Level up your protection against #COVID19. Choose a mask with good fit and filtration.  Learn more on the Get the Most Out of Masking webpage and the Face Covering Fact Sheet.

There are now medicines available to treat people with mild to moderate COVID-19 who are at risk for developing severe COVID-19. The medicines must be prescribed by a healthcare provider. Learn more on the Medications and Treatments page of https://t.co/rZgXeUNb9f.
